 và ham thăng quan tiến chức</a></h3></li></ul><div class="fmsidWidgetNewsBoxAnchor" data-id="355832"> </div><div id="Box-FixFB" class="BoxFix"><div id="toolbox"><ul><li class="facebook"><a class="ButtonImage" href="javascript:$vnn.Utilities.FacebookShare();" title="Chia sẻ lên Facebook"><span>Facebook</span></a></li><li class="google"><a class="ButtonImage" href="javascript:$vnn.Utilities.GoogleShare();" title="Chia sẻ lên Google+"><span>google</span></a></li><li class="comment"><a class="ButtonImage" href="#listComment"><span>Bình luận</span></a></li><li class="like"><span class="fmsidWidgetLike" data-layout="bubble" data-type="article" data-key="vietnamnet.vn_tuanvietnam-dachieu_355832" data-id="355832" data-guid="" data-title="Học văn ở Mỹ, tôi thực sự thấy mình là ‘trung tâm’" data-url="http://vietnamnet.vn/vn/tuanvietnam/dachieu/hoc-van-o-my-toi-thuc-su-thay-minh-la-trung-tam-355832.html" data-thumb="http://imgs.vietnamnet.vn/Images/2017/02/10/15/20170210153922-sider-univ-of-dallas-800x0-c-default.jpg"> </span></li></ul><div class="fb-like" data-href="https://developers.facebook.com/docs/plugins/" data-layout="box_count" data-action="like" data-show-faces="false" data-share="false"> </div></div><div class="star-rating"><span class="fmsidWidgetRating" data-max="5" data-current="0" data-type="article" data-key="vietnamnet.vn_tuanvietnam-dachieu_355832" data-guid="" data-id="355832" data-title="Học văn ở Mỹ, tôi thực sự thấy mình là ‘trung tâm’" data-url="http://vietnamnet.vn/vn/tuanvietnam/dachieu/hoc-van-o-my-toi-thuc-su-thay-minh-la-trung-tam-355832.html" data-thumb="http://imgs.vietnamnet.vn/Images/2017/02/10/15/20170210153922-sider-univ-of-dallas-800x0-c-default.jpg"> </span></div></div><div class="fmsSurvey" wcode="VietNamNet" objid="355832" objtype="Article"> </div><div id="listComment"><div id="BoxBinhLuan" class="fmsidWidgetComment" data-type="article" data-key="vietnamnet.vn_tuanvietnam-dachieu_355832" data-guid="" data-id="355832" data-title="Học văn ở Mỹ, tôi thực sự thấy mình là ‘trung tâm’" data-url="http://vietnamnet.vn/vn/tuanvietnam/dachieu/hoc-van-o-my-toi-thuc-su-thay-minh-la-trung-tam-355832.html" data-thumb="http://imgs.vietnamnet.vn/Images/2017/02/10/15/20170210153922-sider-univ-of-dallas-800x0-c-default.jpg" data-domain="vietnamnet.vn" data-cate="tuanvietnam-dachieu"><span class="hidden"> </span></div></div><div class="none" articletracking="true" id="ai355832" wcode="VietNamNet" categoryalias="tuanvietnam" catname="tuanvietnam" articleid="355832" atitle="Học văn ở Mỹ, tôi thực sự thấy mình là ‘trung tâm’" alead="" atags="" aimg="http://imgs.vietnamnet.vn/Images/2017/02/10/15/20170210153922-sider-univ-of-dallas-800x0-c-default.jpg" adate="15/02/2017"> </div><script type="application/ld+json">
